Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…灯吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为以女人的身体复活会有什么不便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真好!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要对灯的身体做什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的身体!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金Qwaser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯! 灯!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的灵魂与这女人最好的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自己补充圣乳的Qwaser诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的胸部!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\3c&H060608&\pos(600,380)}#17 炎之福音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地期盼着这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰灯的身体!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冬?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来救我的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快逃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是单纯的惹人发笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黄金僭主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的意识取代了这女人的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人感动不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也把你带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子来伺候我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有十年没见了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久呢 凤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类烟火师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金之Qwaser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算利用沉睡于『法贝尔彩蛋』中的回路来除掉我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 要除掉刚觉醒的我倒也不是不可能.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想法不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后你的利刃能碰到我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻求『萨鲁伊·苏之生神女』后得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类所无法持有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你该担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要按照预言那般行动即可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是『贤者』『Qwaser』的使命!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做我们才会得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将同伴作为祭品是神的指引吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的庇佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴被神召换走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭…品?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些使徒一直被蒙在鼓里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『贤者』真正的目的是逼迫亚历山大·尼克拉叶维奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使其登上新的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每击倒一名使徒都会被镌刻上『业』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言者在寻求染血之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向萨鲁伊·苏的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历山大·尼克拉叶维奇·赫尔才是被预言所认定的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且他正在不断地完善着自身的存在!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个受到诅咒的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接受的是祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如我所想的一样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特蕾莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定打倒我的这份决心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会使你变强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你为了被我杀死 故意装成被人控制的样子吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生神女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我没资格做你的搭挡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 请动身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 请获胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢过你所背负的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越自我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『致命者·沙夏』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许你赐予罪人教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉我和利兹的话 你会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒那两个人了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来他会更加接近完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能做出那种事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 凤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你本来想将铁之小鬼培养成你手下的一枚棋子?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是打错了算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来看看你的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冬?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 你怎么这副样子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复成灯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是真正的灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我解开这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没杀掉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太软弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有过颤抖的体验吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又曾有….
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将身体置于严寒彻骨的极寒大气…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之中过的经验吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤 榊一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致命者 沙夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将身体献给天命吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧娅的仇人!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的试炼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试炼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你变得完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用不着你期待!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这水平吗 似乎是我看走眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的话 之前我派来的使徒们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都白白送死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让沙夏变强 你们到底有什么目的??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说当他成为血染之剑后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会引导我们找到萨鲁伊·苏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致命者 沙夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死鸟!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一心只想复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你还依赖这股愤怒与蛮力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就绝对赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了除掉欧娅的仇人!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉你们而活!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭现在的你是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你还依赖自身的复仇怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就发挥不出真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么真正的力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个杀戮者!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为达目的不择手段 双手沾满鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要明白啊 铁之少年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你有想要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是觉得那是幸福的话 就要牢牢把握住!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧咬不放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上一切去守护它即可!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我也要一起战斗…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所以…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}吸取我的生命去战斗吧!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我绝对会保护你们{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你还不明白的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到此为止!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 太软弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我想要保护的东西…有很多!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 真冬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上阶梯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁之少年…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接接看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最大的奥义!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个秘技…会杀掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终审判!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄大 ….
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得保护的东西 并非回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起失去之后的愤怒 即将失去之前所产生的恐惧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能孕育出更为强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏 你竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让我得到了救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自说自话了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是罪人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该受到地狱业火的焚烧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后你要与他一道前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来就在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要和师傅分开!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好你没死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生神女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请祝福你所引导的宿命者们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤那家伙 装半天帅结果不过是个萝莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超好笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许说师傅的坏话!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没有发言的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对你萌生出邪念情感的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心一直处于矛盾的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续了好多年呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不配做殉教者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪他会因为区区山边雄大的怂恿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就背弃了『贤者』的教义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其结果就是这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊 沙夏君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是灯哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想的没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历山大·尼克拉叶维奇·赫尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎很中意这家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 黄金之Qwaser吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤那家伙 最后还真是做了件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是神的旨意吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『鲜血之剑』的持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有一名使徒的生命献出了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 『黄女之卵』!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言即将成真!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!终于要孵化了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『利刃之生神女』!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧寄宿在我体内的,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『利刃之生神女』的力量啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那座铁塔上?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区异端者!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇女之证是属于我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会交给你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铜之『Qwaser』吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分不清场合的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 彩蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呿 真扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你连靠近我都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冬 快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复原样吧!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制还不完全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 这边请!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冬!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『鲜血之剑』的完成 虽然几经波折 总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金之…Qwaser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冬的花蕾肆意盛放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬の蕾花咲く頃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无边的天际银辉闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空の色は銀に輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气战栗 百花缭乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大気は奮え風は花弁を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如羽毛般飘散 随风消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽根のように吹き散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱惑他 怂恿他 接近那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘い誘え彼の場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金光璀璨的桃源之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金に輝く桃源郷は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吞噬一切的天堂亦是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て飲み込む天か地獄か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉寂在这冰封的时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍ったままの刻の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强忍寂寞的你在等待谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独に耐えて誰を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 我是否有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神よ私は罪ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湛蓝的瞳仁究竟映照出何物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧い瞳は何を映すの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古老的传说低吟传诵 他亦无所动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古の物語でも彼を奮わせられない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃无边的寒冰之下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深く深い氷の下には
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重获新生的圣洁之光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生まれたての聖なる光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必指引着他前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうか彼を導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这双手去扰乱激情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その手で情熱を　かき乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 理所当然的事情才有诱惑的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大抵当たり前のことには 誘惑の価値がある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:22:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法割舍的思念 还有那残酷的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:22:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,割り切れない想い　そして無残な未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然被窥伺的这份孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然狙われた淋しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都是由你而起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴方のせいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在橱窗前看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飾り窓に見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的亡灵是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去の亡霊は誰よ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走过来便能知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来れば解る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拥紧那已呈深黑的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黒い心臓抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在此处 让我去倾听心跳的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その場限り 声を聞かせておくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这会不再相见的地方传来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二度と　二度と逢えない場所から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懊悔起爱上他人的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だからひとをあいしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あやもちをくやむほど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信徒们欢欣鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂信者は喜ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以将一切都藏进心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから全て胸のなか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随意呼喊神之名的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,むやみに神の名を語る愚かしさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blank out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おろかしさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家福总会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体像がいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在曲终人散的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終わる頃に現れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金僭主!
